<i>noun</i>: 큰물 [큰물], 억수 [억쑤] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>큰물 [큰물]</dt><br>
<dd>1. bigger arena; big water</dd><br>
<dd>(비유적으로) 사람이 활동하는 장소가 크고 넓은 곳.</dd><br>
<dd>(figurative) A big, spacious place for human activity.</dd><br>
<dd>2. torrents</dd><br>
<dd>비가 많이 내려서 갑자기 크게 불어난 강이나 개천의 물.</dd><br>
<dd>The water in a river or stream that has suddenly risen due to a heavy rain and is moving quickly.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>억수 [억쑤]</dt><br>
<dd>1. heavy rain; pouring rain</dd><br>
<dd>물이 쏟아지듯이 세차게 많이 내리는 비.</dd><br>
<dd>Torrential rain like the pouring of water.</dd><br>
<dd>2. torrents; flood; pouring</dd><br>
<dd>정도가 아주 심함.</dd><br>
<dd>A state of being very extraordinary in quantity, extent, etc.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>